Four Types of Drift Detection. 1) Quality Drift: Answer Quality over Time (line chart with baseline, alert at -10%). 2) Data Drift: Input Distribution Changes (histograms: baseline vs current, KL Divergence). 3) Cost Drift: Unexpected Cost Increases (bar chart: cost/query trend, alert at +20%). 4) Performance Drift: Rising Latencies/Error Rates (P95 line chart, alert at +50%). Each with German labels, alert thresholds marked.